qas.question: What language is parle or tem ?
What language  is parlo or temo ?

context:
In verbs, 1st person present indicative desinence is -e (∅ in verbs of the 2nd and 3rd conjugation), or -o.
E.g. parle, tem, sent (<a0_0>Valencian<a0_0/>); parlo, temo, sento (<a1_0>Northwestern<a1_0/>). In verbs, 1st person present indicative desinence is -o, -i or ∅ in all conjugations.
E.g. parlo (Central), parl (<a2_0>Balearic<a2_0/>), parli (<a3_0>Northern<a3_0/>), ('I speak').
